        "### Execution & Effects\n",
        "\n",
        "The prediction pipeline (`entsoe_predict` calling `get_model_prediction` and `make_plot`) performs the following actions:\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Model Loading\n",
        "\n",
        "Retrieves the **latest trained model** (highest iteration) from `~/spotforecast2_cache`.\n",
        "Ensures the model is valid and implements the `package_prediction` interface.\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Prediction Package Generation\n",
        "\n",
        "Prediction Package Generation (`get_model_prediction`) generates a standardized dictionary containing:\n",
        "\n",
        "Prediction Package Generation (`get_model_prediction`) generates a standardized dictionary containing the components shown in @tbl-predict-entsoe-package.\n",
        "\n",
        "| Key | Type | Description |\n",
        "| :--- | :--- | :--- |\n",
        "| `train_actual` | `pd.Series` | Historical ground truth data used for training (aligned with `train_pred`). |\n",
        "| `train_pred` | `pd.Series` | In-sample model predictions on the training set (for goodness-of-fit). |\n",
        "| `future_actual` | `pd.Series` | Ground truth data for the immediate past/validation window (if available). |\n",
        "| `future_pred` | `pd.Series` | Out-of-sample model predictions for the validation window and future horizon. |\n",
        "| `future_forecast` | `pd.Series` | Benchmark forecast (e.g., source ENTSO-E data) for comparison (optional). |\n",
        "| `metrics_train` | `Dict[str, float]` | Training performance metrics (MAE, MAPE). |\n",
        "| `metrics_future` | `Dict[str, float]` | Test performance metrics over the full prediction horizon. |\n",
        "| `metrics_future_one_day` | `Dict[str, float]` | Test performance metrics specifically for the first 24 hours. |\n",
        "| `metrics_forecast` | `Dict[str, float]` | Benchmark performance metrics (if benchmark is present). |\n",
        "| `validation_passed` | `bool` | Flag indicating if the model meets safety/quality criteria (e.g., no negative loads). |\n",
        "\n",
        ": Prediction Package Components {#tbl-predict-entsoe-package}\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "### Metric Computation Window\n",
        "\n",
        "The prediction package computes metrics over two distinct windows:\n",
        "\n",
        "- **24h metrics** (`metrics_future_one_day`): Calculated on the first 24 hours only (`future_pred.iloc[:24]`)\n",
        "- **Full horizon metrics** (`metrics_future`): Calculated on the entire prediction window (`predict_size * refit_size` hours)\n",
        "\n",
        "With the current configuration (`predict_size=24`, `refit_size=7`, `end_train_default='2022-01-05'`), the full horizon is **168 hours (7 days)**. The ENTSO-E dataset has ample data available after this training cutoff, so the 24h and full horizon metrics **will differ** because they evaluate different time ranges (24 hours vs 168 hours).\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "#### Visualization (`make_plot`)\n",
        "\n",
        "Generates a Plotly figure (see @fig-entsoe-predict) with the following structure:\n",
        "\n",
        "**Plot Structure & X-Axis Range:**\n",
        "\n",
        "*   **Left Region**: Historical training period showing model fit quality (in-sample predictions).\n",
        "*   **Right Region**: Future prediction window showing out-of-sample forecasts.\n",
        "*   **X-Axis Range**: Automatically focused on `[end_training - 1 day, latest_data_point]` to highlight the critical transition from training to prediction.\n",
        "*   **Vertical Marker**: Black dashed line at `end_training` timestamp separating historical from future.\n",
        "\n",
        "**Plot Lines & Legend:**\n",
        "\n",
        "| Legend Entry | Line Style | Data Source | Purpose | Embedded Metrics |\n",
        "| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |\n",
        "| **Total system load (actual)** | Solid line + markers | Ground truth (`train_actual` + `future_actual`) | Shows actual energy demand across entire time range | None |\n",
        "| **Total system load (model prediction)** | Solid line + markers | Model output (`train_pred` + `future_pred`) | Shows model's predictions for both training and future periods | Training MAE/MAPE, Prediction (24h) MAE/MAPE, Prediction (full horizon) MAE/MAPE |\n",
        "| **Benchmark Forecast (e.g., ENTSOE)** | Solid line + markers | External forecast (`future_forecast`) | Provides comparison baseline from ENTSO-E or other source (optional) | Benchmark (24h) MAE/MAPE, Benchmark (full horizon) MAE/MAPE |\n",
        "| **Actual (last week)** | Dashed line + markers | Time-shifted actual data (`y_actual.shift(7*24)`) | Reveals weekly seasonality patterns for context | None |\n",
        "\n",
        "**Layout Configuration:**\n",
        "\n",
        "*   **Title**: \"Energy Demand Prediction\"\n",
        "*   **Y-Axis**: \"Load [MW]\"\n",
