        "Note that Approach 1 and Approach 2 yield identical predictive metrics. This is by design: both rely on the exact same estimator defaults and the identical training data window. The difference lies strictly in system architecture (lazy fitting during inference versus explicit pre-fitting during the batch training pipeline).\n",
        "\n",
        "### Approach 3: Tune, Train, and Predict\n",
        "\n",
        "For optimal performance, the spotforecast2 package provides the full orchestration capabilities to tune the hyperparameters using Bayesian optimization, train the model with the best discovered parameters, and serialize the optimized artifact. \n",
